videos.description: Corey Clement run for a loss of 1 yard to the LSU 24
videos.headline: LSU defense stuffs Wisconsin on 4th down.

videos.description: LSU's defense comes up big when Rickey Jefferson intercepts Wisconsin QB Bart Houston in the end zone ending the Badgers' scoring threat.
videos.headline: LSU intercepts Wisconsin in end zone

videos.description: Todd McShay leaps into the Lambeau Field stands during the LSU-Wisconsin game.
videos.headline: McShay goes up for a Lambeau Leap

videos.description: Leonard Fournette run for no gain to the LSU 45
videos.headline: Wisconsin stops Fournette on 4th and 1

videos.description: LSU Head Coach Les Miles Halftime Interview
videos.headline: LSU Head Coach Les Miles Halftime Interview

videos.description: Brandon Harris pass intercepted Derrick Tindal return for 43 yds to the LSU 31
videos.headline: B. Harris pass intercepted,D. Tindal return  for 43 yds

videos.description: Corey Clement run for 4 yds to the LSU 1
videos.headline: Wisconsin breaks through, scores first TD of game

videos.description: Trailing 13-0, LSU turns to its defense when Tre'Davious White makes the interception and returns it all the way back for the touchdown, cutting Wisconsin's lead to six.
videos.headline: Pick-six has LSU back in the game

videos.description: Brandon Harris pass complete to Travin Dural for 10 yds for a TD
videos.headline: LSU converts turnover into quick touchdown to take the lead.

videos.description: Bart Houston pass complete to George Rushing for 11 yds George Rushing fumbled, forced by Donte Jackson, recovered by LSU Tre'Davious White  , return for 6 yds to the Wisc 41
videos.headline: LSU's defense forces another turnover
R. Gaglianone 47 yd FG GOOD gives Wisconsin the lead late in the 4th quarter.

videos.description: Leonard Fournette leaves game with injury
videos.headline: Leonard Fournette leaves game with injury

videos.description: Trailing by two late in the fourth quarter, LSU quarterback Brandon Harris is picked off by D'Cota Dixon, which seals the upset win for Wisconsin. After the play, Josh Boutte is ejected following a vicious hit on Dixon.
videos.headline: LSU's Boutte ejected after hit following game-sealing INT

videos.description: After Wisconsin grabs the game-sealing interception, LSU's Josh Boutte takes out his frustration with a vicious late hit and gets ejected.
videos.headline: LSU's Boutte gets ejected for vicious late hit

videos.description: Badgers kicker Rafael Gaglianone went 3-for-3 on the game, including a 47-yard field goal in the final minutes of the fourth quarter that gave Wisconsin a 16-14 upset win over LSU.
videos.headline: Wisconsin stuns Fournette, No. 5 LSU in opener
